rows.label: xs00070100_MSG0001
rows.name: Your movements were pretty good back there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs00070100_MSG0002
rows.name:
Your weapon handling also seems fine.
At this rate, it looks like you could get a job soon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs00070100_MSG0003
rows.name:
Glad you're interested.
I'm sure there's something that would be a good fit for you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs00070100_MSG0004
rows.name:
It's up to you whether you take it or not.
You can decide after you hear more about it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs00070100_MSG0005
rows.name:
We can discuss the details once we get somewhere safe.
Come on, let's keep moving.[ST:wait ]
